--- !u!114 &1040186582
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1040186580}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 6d914fbda925c2948b560a7854935810, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  backgroundImage: {fileID: 996724200}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1199275183}
  textContainer: {fileID: 1792452427}
  endingPanelGroup: {fileID: 996724202}
  endingSlides:
  - paragraphText: 'I entered the engine room.

      When my eyes adjusted to the
      dark, I saw...'
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: The engine was not an engine anymore, but had become twisted and
      entangled in this fungus that had spread everywhere.
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: It pulled the walls and machinery of the rooms inwards towards
      itself and collapsed into a single, burning center.
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: Flames licked out of its fungal mouth and cast the room in shadow,
      into a darkness that grew much further than the room should allow.
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: 'As I stared into its burning esophagus, I felt a tug to step
      ever closer to its maw.

      And with every step, I heard its call to enter.'
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: And with every step, I found the flames more and more...
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: b e a u t i f u l
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c1d329fbbf992204cb4954014a84b1d3, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 1
  - paragraphText: 'I didn''t know where the fungus''s desires ended and mine began.

      But
      with one more step, I could...'
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: e n t e r
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: aaea66086f556a24894a8a98763accde, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: 4457835537561387818, guid: febe32599564f344490be4cba01e1835, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
    delayAfterFinished: 3
  - paragraphText: 'On stardate [REDACTED], the Galactic Federation for Earth received
      a distress signal from Research Vessel #37282. '
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2291391810689640612, guid: 9597db52a42aa4540af93ce4e2cadd7d, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: -200}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: On stardate [REDACTED], the Federation lost contact with Research
      Vessel #37282.
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2291391810689640612, guid: e723a3d9d7bbb3546bd2e925a0a7ae9c, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: -200}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: On stardate [REDACTED], the Federation made contact again with
      Research Vessel #37282 and received a message.
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2291391810689640612, guid: 1cd0f18916b4984418a83c29eba1b42f, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: -200}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: 'When decoded it read:'
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2291391810689640612, guid: 1cd0f18916b4984418a83c29eba1b42f, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: -200}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: i t ' s s o b e a u t i f u l . b e a u t y b e y o n d\nt i m
      e b e a u t y b e y o n d e y e s . i w i l l s h o w y o u b e a u t y i n
      a h a n d f u l o f s o u l s .
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: aaea66086f556a24894a8a98763accde, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2291391810689640612, guid: 3162228d8c2cf374b918e76338beaf4f, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: -200}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  - paragraphText: Research Vessel #37282 is approaching Earth at 0.2c and accelerating.
    fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 3b4a83765af3a5f478ad28cc26197aab, type: 2}
    backgroundSprite: {fileID: -2291391810689640612, guid: 3162228d8c2cf374b918e76338beaf4f, type: 3}
    textAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: -200}
    delayAfterFinished: 2
  typeSpeed: 0.04
